<plot>The ring of the phone launches another hellish April Fool for Stafford. He accepts his friend's invitation to a night on the town, where yet another cruel prank lies in wait. Later, drunk and distraught, Stafford is drawn to a siren: the love of his life. And by last call, love will turn to deceit, friends will become enemies and the games being played will make it hard to tell who's really out for revenge and who is...the April Fool.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?043956</url></doc>
